node.title: COVID-19 latest: Omicron 'raging through the world', Holland plunged into lockdown
node.content: ["Here's the latest on the COVID-19 pandemic from around the world.\n", "White House medical adviser Anthony Fauci is urging people travelling over the holidays to get booster shots and always wear masks in crowded public spaces. He described Omicron as \"raging through the world\", and said travelling will increase the risk of infection even among vaccinated people.\u00a0", "The impact of the virus is spreading across the US, with hospitalisations jumping, sports games being rescheduled and entertainment venues canceling shows.", "Since the start of the month, both US COVID cases and deaths have risen about 50 percent and the number of hospitalised COVID patients climbed 26 percent,\u00a0according to a Reuters tally."]
